<normalizedToken originalValue="“Missouri,”">&quot;Missouri,&quot;</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Alabama”">&quot;Alabama&quot;</normalizedToken>
(Bousquet 1987a: 127-128), and northern Florida (Hamilton, Okaloosa, and Taylor Counties, CNC).
</paragraph>
